[LEGAL CLAUSE 01] - TECHNICAL SPECS & ARCHITECTURAL DEPENDENCIES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This system operates under advanced architectural specifications including:
  * AUTHENTICATION LAYER: Asynchronous JSON Web Tokens (JWT) Engine
  * FILE INGESTION PIPELINE: Cloudinary cloud-native asset storage
  * LOCAL STATE TELEMETRY: Redux Toolkit (RTK) global slices & middleware
  * BACKEND ENGINE: Node.js / Express.js optimized routing

